 src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/221232_a1bbfbd5f1039a2fc65b875bc0686f44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F221232_a1bbfbd5f1039a2fc65b875bc0686f44.jpg&h=5822701c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/221234_3542176a56637ee2ef4b12decacadbf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F221234_3542176a56637ee2ef4b12decacadbf4.jpg&h=066191ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗佛教陳榮根紀念學校證實收到家長投訴指校內一名男主任向小六女生傳示愛短訊，但該主任未被停職，校方亦未有報警。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/221326_ff5da8fd95ded788ae292ec30f7bffd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F221326_ff5da8fd95ded788ae292ec30f7bffd2.jpg&h=1972c3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/221328_091e0879606a49856e03c2f5f3a8f940.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F221328_091e0879606a49856e03c2f5f3a8f940.jpg&h=3143f7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/221329_f6bc3b60bdc1bee3dfabff86c94bfdcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F221329_f6bc3b60bdc1bee3dfabff86c94bfdcb.jpg&h=ddff9eba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/221330_d85cca428033cb26bc0a5f1e5a702a7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F221330_d85cca428033cb26bc0a5f1e5a702a7a.jpg&h=02a6428e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/221330_21e2dc9537a0a813f873072780954596.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F221330_21e2dc9537a0a813f873072780954596.jpg&h=50d3fba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【更新：新增教育局回應】<br />\n有網民周一（7月31日）在facebook群組「盡在元朗」貼文，聲稱發現其剛小學畢業的妹妹校內有一名男主任，經常私下傳短訊給妹妹，部分用言語甚為露骨，如向其妹表示「你先係我女神」、「好掛住你」、「I❤U」等等，該男主任甚至曾稱自己身在其家門外。發文的網民指，「細妹有跟我說，那主任會在全部同學面前拖住佢，撓住佢，令到佢好唔舒服，但因為佢係老師，佢無say no」，更質疑「呢啲身體接觸是一個男老師應對一個小學生所做的嗎？」不過有關貼文今日已經被刪走。<br />\n<br />\n發文的網民表示，她曾向妹妹就讀的小學舉報事件，亦曾與該名男主任當面對質，對方聲稱「只係當我細妹是女兒般看待」，但她認為不可接受，亦批評該小學校長的回覆「等於無回覆，仲不停話傾傾傾」，她希望提醒家長們留意下子女的舉動，她又在私人fb戶口貼出8幅妹妹與該名男主任的WhatsApp對話截圖。不少看過截圖的網民都認為事態嚴重，建議事主報警，本報嘗試透過fb聯絡發文的事主，但暫未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n有網民懷疑事件涉及元朗佛教陳榮根紀念學校。本報向該校校長陳滿林查詢，陳承認早前接獲涉事家長舉報，事件涉事該校一名男性主任，因現時正值暑假，故該男主任未被停職，但陳拒絕透露對方的資料。他稱有留意到有關網上言論，校方和教董會均對事件甚為關注，已啟動危機處理機制，由駐校社工、心理學家、校董及校長等成員跟進事件，亦已成立調查委員會調查事件，成員包括校董、校長及學務管理委員會。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否有包庇該名男主任時，陳指事件仍在調查中，對事件未有定案，亦拒透露網上流傳的短訊截圖是否由該名男主任傳出。至於會否就事件報警，他只稱校方會就調查結果作出相應行動。<br />\n<br />\n教育局回覆指，曾經接獲有關查詢，並已即時與學校聯絡，正了解及跟進事件。局方又稱非常重視教師的專業操守，強調教師的職責是教育學生，言論和行為應合乎專業操守和社會期望，而《香港教育專業守則》亦有指出一個專業教育工作者應與學生建立互相信任和尊重的關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170801&amp;guid=57029250&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170801%26guid%3D57029250%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=eThoJcB1ACfYqYpccgV6HsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=9bd88993\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170801%26guid%3D57029250%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=5364ed25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170801&amp;guid=57029250&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a></blockquote><br />\n佢有冇上連登動漫台???"},{"pid":"6f57ee4b014642e21458a412facbc895fccfc2b2","tid":343540,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:42:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f21a004fcee6cbd520c72d32fdc0ccf352e5453","tid":343540,"uid":2216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:45:02.000Z","msg":"背景個男仔乜水？"},{"pid":"992130389ea6c735faf3e4d72dc6204a784fec8b","tid":343540,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"咁撚仆街嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9935a0982bb862139fc5ea11df6f5b0b8db9bccc","tid":343540,"uid":36403,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:20:47.000Z","msg":"個女仔係我同班同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31182327c1130521c18174be40e0f41f7c719623","tid":343540,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個女仔係我同班同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小六上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條女邊班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e064157cf5197421de931f37c434c175953ca46a","tid":343540,"uid":36759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>背景個男仔乜水？</blockquote><br />\n薛之謙"},{"pid":"dd61f33cc274d2bcb069026d28cd210763ba449b","tid":343540,"uid":59690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>據講呢個主任就快退休，<br />\n而且佢廿年來都係咁對啲學生。<br />\n對男學生就好惡好嚴厲，<br />\n扯耳仔罰跑圈跑到虛脫；<br />\n對女嘅就顯得好好人、好關心咁，噓寒問暖口花花。<br />\n到啲女學生畢左業就會係咁send whatsapp話掛住佢地，問返啲舊生就知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老紳士</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c20b2e08bce0aa030084351bde57797286b19a","tid":343540,"uid":117516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"畢左業7,8年 我覺得係姓譚果個主任<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},