te><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbcc50910a168a2d5058c0ce3e02be6e0d0febb","tid":343540,"uid":9950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:20:35.000Z","msg":"訓導主任帶頭唔守紀律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2e5f6fb568c613cf4b5d33fb436499262312c8","tid":343540,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:21:08.000Z","msg":"違反專業關警察咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8efe0ad2f7a8f6048ae08cc4860e614fdf18ae","tid":343540,"uid":9950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:26:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>違反專業關警察咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入唔到罪 名都臭撚哂架<br />\n份工無 退休金無 唔洗撈"},{"pid":"24d4a3f49888df5e080ac4da551ae51eb22701c5","tid":343540,"uid":9950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd1d2596e6a1995173aa763d20d7c3687b23285","tid":343540,"uid":26509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T02:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>畢左業7,8年 我覺得係姓譚果個主任<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一睇到篇新聞都估緊係咪自己小學 今日新聞出就估撚到邊個<br />\n我都覺得係姓譚果個*訓導主任 (我讀果陣係)<br />\n首先我都估佢就退休，我啊哥讀果陣佢已經教緊 應該15年前<br />\n佢對男學生 同 女學生真係好大分別 <br />\n女學生唔會罵佢之外 仲好好咁訓導 <br />\n男學生? 即場屌到你一面屁 之外有D重犯 捉上講台企 睇下佢D訓導方法幾撚ON9<br />\n<br />\n樓上有人話姓麥 我都比佢教過maths 佢男女都即場噴都你成面血 成層都聽到<br />\n你份功課做得差又扔簿<br />\n但畢業果年佢D脾氣已經收返好多 雖然都屌人<br />\n<br />\n利申: 未搬學校 下午校 畢業9年</blockquote><br />\n仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地可能係同學"},{"pid":"64d75a2b9e7a44def7ec25f74a0a6a41a4259923","tid":343540,"uid":5462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T02:13:45.000Z","msg":"我同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27c3b1378370c3855aa8c82f27b784b1a26fc54","tid":343540,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T02:19:14.000Z","msg":"主任好似好正 好想俾佢屌"},{"pid":"f763d2b2efed136483ff90569d46653eb20210df","tid":343540,"uid":24909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T02:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我師姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多校友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33b86ae892a1889d2180688eab6d7e3d087958e","tid":343540,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T03:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.bcwkms.edu.hk/web/page.action?id=121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bcwkms.edu.hk%2Fweb%2Fpage.action%3Fid%3D121&d=eThoJcB1ACfYqYpccgV6HsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=72c6234b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bcwkms.edu.hk/web/page.action?id=121</a>大家估下邊位呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下午校個班阿蛇miss 都仲係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f8a333bb80a36a16cbb65c9ceeef28bd1d1110","tid":343540,"uid":126347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"畢業左十尻幾年，重記得佢同一個女學生行出女廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}